reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect stationary set for various purposes AND super cute
reviews.reviewText: Although this stationary set is advertised for kids and teens, as an adult I found this to be exactly what I was looking for. As someone who is huge into journaling and organizing AND as a fan of cinnamoroll, this was amazing! It comes with a cinnamoroll journal, 5 pens with cute art of various sanrio characters that I shared with 4 of my other journaling friends as we all wrote together, 4 sticky note pads which was great for work, some cute cinnamoroll badges and paper clips which were great for displaying on my desk and bookmarking pages, a HUGE variety of cinnamoroll stickers which was perfect for putting into my diary, a lanyard which I put my bus pass in (and the case is pretty hard too) and a pencil pouch which I used to store some of my jewelry charms since I like to make charms. Now I feel like everything is organized AND cute!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super cute Cinnamonroll Stationary Set
reviews.reviewText: I had received this set right after thanksgiving yesterday and wore one of the little cinnamonroll pins to go meet up with my eldest daughter and my 3 grandchildren. The kids all liked my cute bunny pin I was wearing on my sweater. So, I have hints on things to buy for them this year for Christmas and their upcoming birthdays. Even my grandson liked the bunny and said he would like one the same good thing cartoons are not gender snobs. The rest of this set included many items shaped like the cinnamonroll bunny, which includes paperclips, stickers, pens with other hello kitty characters, sticky note pad, Notebook, 4pins to wear, lanyard with a photo tag all included in this super cute set. Good for anyone who loves all the hello kitty characters doesn't matter what gender or profession or age. I will be buying these again as gifts for family.
